description:
Which matters more when it comes to entertaining and educating youth: nature or media? Being outside is great for the mind and the body, but what about the benefits of technology? Join Sam Neves and Busi Khumalo in this episode of #ANNInDepth as they discuss the importance of the outdoors in youth ministries—especially for boys.

For the full episode, copy and paste the link into your browser: https://youtu.be/Q0ao-bZQZ_E
